@ncw 
Thanks for getting back to me so quickly. I already have a service account set up using rclone. I can only add to the service account drive, which is not what I want to do. From what I understand, I need to impersonate the user so I can add to their drive. I don't see a way of doing this via rclone. 

The SDK would be much to slow for this. I have 5TB of data to upload. Maybe what I need to do is use a service account and set up a domain wide authority in the developer console. I'm not sure which direction to go here.
